Paratype young females. Morphological characteristics of specimen similar to holotype female, except: main flagellum of antenna 1 (
Fig. 29
) with 1 seta (arrowhead) on inner distal corner of basal article, in addition to 1–2 plumose setae on outer margin; uropod peduncle length 1.1 times length of exopod, the latter with 7 setae on its inner and apical margins and 3 setae on its dorsal surface. Uropod endopod damaged during collection.
